<br>
We have an enchanter now, she's level 50.<br>
<br>
Added a few more melee classes, and have a ton of shamans (I guess they all want to get familiar with Fear to do the demis.  I doubt I'll be doing them this time).<br>
<br>
We do have a FD'er available.  <br>
<br>
Might have another wizard, so potentially 3 groups can evac.<br>
<br>
No necro's though, so having a trainer run everything to the Northeast corner seems unlikely (no summon corpse or COH).<br>
<br>
Probably what we'll try is a 3 group West wall charge.  Send the 3 toughest groups in with the evaccers and have them evac out before anyone dies.<br>
<br>
One thing I saw that interested me, can you really make a /target scareling button and have it work?  that would be really useful for our main tank if so...<br>
